plot: Gabriel and Micheal attack New Delphia. David joins the V1 rebels against Claire and Vega.

After discovering the truth behind Julian's army, Alex confronts an impossible decision as he spearheads a plan to intercept Michael and Gabriel, who have breached the walls of New Delphi in pursuit of their mutual target. Claire begins the negotiation process with the revolting V1's as David attempts to restore his legacy by any means necessary. Finally, a familiar face returns to Vega just in time to see it change forever.
